Not always, but when
you least expect it, we'll be there.

249
00:09:08,019 --> 00:09:10,510
任何一个你想结交的人，甚至是交谈过的
Anyone you try to make friends with
or even talk to,

250
00:09:10,688 --> 00:09:13,143
反正是有过任何交集的人
other than ordering a hot dog
or something,

251
00:09:13,316 --> 00:09:17,479
