But I am not you.

258
00:09:35,629 --> 00:09:37,918
感谢上帝
Thank God.

259
00:09:38,090 --> 00:09:40,498
所以做你想做的事吧
So do what you want.

260
00:09:40,676 --> 00:09:43,167
